{
 "uid": "devnet-apis-validating",
 "title": "Devnet - Validating Pair APIs (besu + teku)",
 "description": "Every interface of the validating pair in one place. An EL+CL pair exposes exactly three API surfaces: the EL's JSON-RPC (external), the engine API between them (internal, CL drives EL), and the CL's Beacon REST API (external). The top row is the health summary that the SLOs build on; the sections below break each surface down. Note this pair's CL (teku) sees almost no external REST traffic - its validators are driven internally - which is the opposite of the archive pair.",
 "tags": [
  "devnet",
  "api",
  "validating-pair"
 ],
 "timezone": "browser",
 "schemaVersion": 39,
 "refresh": "10s",
 "time": {
  "from": "now-1h",
  "to": "now"
 },
 "panels": [
  {
   "type": "row",
   "title": "Health summary (the SLI candidates)",
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 1,
    "w": 24,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 0
   },
   "panels": []
  },
  {
   "type": "stat",
   "title": "besu RPC req/s",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 5,
    "w": 6,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 1
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum(rate(besu_rpc_request_time_count[5m]))"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "stat",
   "title": "besu RPC errors / min",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 5,
    "w": 6,
    "x": 6,
    "y": 1
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum(rate(besu_rpc_errors_count_total[5m])) * 60"
    }
   ],
   "fieldConfig": {
    "defaults": {
     "thresholds": {
      "mode": "absolute",
      "steps": [
       {
        "color": "green",
        "value": null
       },
       {
        "color": "yellow",
        "value": 1
       },
       {
        "color": "red",
        "value": 10
       }
      ]
     }
    },
    "overrides": []
   }
  },
  {
   "type": "stat",
   "title": "engine API errors / min",
   "description": "forkchoice + newPayload errors - the CL-EL link failing.",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 5,
    "w": 6,
    "x": 12,
    "y": 1
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum(rate(beacon_engine_requests_total{job=\"teku\",outcome=\"error\",method=~\"forkchoice_updated.*|new_payload.*\"}[5m])) * 60"
    }
   ],
   "fieldConfig": {
    "defaults": {
     "thresholds": {
      "mode": "absolute",
      "steps": [
       {
        "color": "green",
        "value": null
       },
       {
        "color": "red",
        "value": 0.1
       }
      ]
     }
    },
    "overrides": []
   }
  },
  {
   "type": "stat",
   "title": "teku REST calls / min",
   "description": "Sparse by design: this pair's validators are managed internally, so its Beacon REST API has almost no external traffic.",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 5,
    "w": 6,
    "x": 18,
    "y": 1
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum(rate(validator_beacon_node_requests_total{job=\"teku\"}[5m])) * 60"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "row",
   "title": "1 - besu JSON-RPC (external: wallets / dapps)",
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 1,
    "w": 24,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 6
   },
   "panels": []
  },
  {
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "RPC request rate",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 7,
    "w": 8,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 7
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum(rate(besu_rpc_request_time_count[5m]))",
     "legendFormat": "req/s"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "RPC latency (p50 / p95 / p99)",
   "description": "besu exposes request time as a summary with quantiles.",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 7,
    "w": 8,
    "x": 8,
    "y": 7
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "besu_rpc_request_time{quantile=\"0.5\"}",
     "legendFormat": "p50"
    },
    {
     "refId": "B",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "besu_rpc_request_time{quantile=\"0.95\"}",
     "legendFormat": "p95"
    },
    {
     "refId": "C",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "besu_rpc_request_time{quantile=\"0.99\"}",
     "legendFormat": "p99"
    }
   ],
   "fieldConfig": {
    "defaults": {
     "unit": "s"
    },
    "overrides": []
   }
  },
  {
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "RPC errors/min & active connections",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 7,
    "w": 8,
    "x": 16,
    "y": 7
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum(rate(besu_rpc_errors_count_total[5m])) * 60",
     "legendFormat": "errors/min"
    },
    {
     "refId": "B",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "besu_rpc_active_http_connection_count",
     "legendFormat": "active connections"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "row",
   "title": "2 - engine API (internal: teku drives besu)",
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 1,
    "w": 24,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 14
   },
   "panels": []
  },
  {
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "engine calls / min by method",
   "description": "forkchoice_updated sets the head, new_payload validates a block, get_payload builds one when teku proposes.",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 7,
    "w": 12,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 15
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum by (method) (rate(beacon_engine_requests_total{job=\"teku\"}[5m])) * 60",
     "legendFormat": "{{method}}"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "get_payload latency distribution (block build)",
   "description": "teku pre-buckets each engine call by latency. This is the block-build call on the proposal deadline; weight shifting to higher buckets means besu is slow to build.",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 7,
    "w": 12,
    "x": 12,
    "y": 15
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum by (interval) (rate(beacon_engine_requests_total{job=\"teku\",method=\"get_payloadV4\"}[5m])) * 60",
     "legendFormat": "{{interval}} ms"
    }
   ]
  },
  {
   "type": "row",
   "title": "3 - teku Beacon REST API (external - sparse here)",
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 1,
    "w": 24,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 22
   },
   "panels": []
  },
  {
   "type": "text",
   "title": "",
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 3,
    "w": 24,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 23
   },
   "options": {
    "mode": "markdown",
    "content": "**This pair's Beacon REST API carries almost no traffic**, and that is expected, not a fault. teku's validators are driven internally (prysm connects to it, not external clients), so its `/eth/v1/...` REST surface is idle. The rich Beacon REST view lives on the **archive pair** dashboard, where lighthouse serves remote-vc over REST. Shown below for completeness."
   }
  },
  {
   "type": "timeseries",
   "title": "teku REST calls / min by method",
   "datasource": {
    "type": "prometheus",
    "uid": "prometheus"
   },
   "gridPos": {
    "h": 6,
    "w": 24,
    "x": 0,
    "y": 26
   },
   "targets": [
    {
     "refId": "A",
     "datasource": {
      "type": "prometheus",
      "uid": "prometheus"
     },
     "expr": "sum by (method) (rate(validator_beacon_node_requests_total{job=\"teku\"}[5m])) * 60",
     "legendFormat": "{{method}}"
    }
   ]
  }
 ]
}